::Aerotaur::
       He gulps at Windlord's message.  "Sir, in short, the Plague will cause 
minor inconveniences at first, leading to hallucinations, then finally to 
rust.  I understand it to be very painful.  The victim's body just wastes 
away.  It is not unlike the Bubonic Plague of Earth history.  It killed 
nearly a third of the population of Cybertron.  I was vaccinated when I was 
still young but it was still untested when I left home... I don't even know 
if it's still in my system."  He shudders involuntarily.  "If that pod was 
rusting as the little one said it was ... the Plague is here.  It is only a 
matter of time."

--part1_2f.3600faaf.2b981d3c_boundary
